name: The Vault

skill: Dealing Ether DMG using an EX Special Attack, Chain Attack, or Ultimate increases all squad members' DMG against the target by 15%/17.5%/20%/22%/24% and increases the equipper's Energy Regen by 0.5/0.58/0.65/0.72/0.8/s for 2s. Passive effects of the same name do not stack.
